<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:20:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>德国八月出口增长，不顾下降预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-august-2024-10-09/</link><description>周三官方数据显示，由于美国需求强劲，德国八月份出口增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:07:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-august-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>东盟在老挝举行峰会，泰国提出应对缅甸危机的新计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-holds-summit-laos-thailand-floats-new-plan-myanmar-crisis-2024-10-09/</link><description>东南亚领导人周三在老挝举行峰会，预计将找到解决缅甸日益恶化的内战的方法，在地区和平努力进展甚微后，泰国将提出新的政治解决途径。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 05:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-holds-summit-laos-thailand-floats-new-plan-myanmar-crisis-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国股市接受现实检验；欧洲颤抖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-09/</link><description>汤姆·威斯布鲁克 (Tom Westbrook) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 04:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，大多数台湾人认为中国不太可能在未来五年内入侵</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/most-taiwanese-believe-china-unlikely-invade-coming-five-years-poll-shows-2024-10-09/</link><description>台湾最高军事智库周三的一项民意调查显示，大多数台湾人认为中国不太可能在未来五年内入侵，但确实认为北京对这个民主岛屿构成严重威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 04:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/most-taiwanese-believe-china-unlikely-invade-coming-five-years-poll-shows-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>现代汽车在印度首次公开募股定价为 30 亿美元，每股价格为 1,865-1,960 卢比</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hyundai-prices-3-bln-india-ipo-1865-1960-rupees-per-share-2024-10-09/</link><description>《金融快报》周三刊登的一则广告显示，现代汽车印度公司已将其首次公开募股 (IPO) 的价格范围设定为 1,865 卢比（22 美元）至 1,960 卢比（23 美元），该股将于下周开始接受认购。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 03:43:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hyundai-prices-3-bln-india-ipo-1865-1960-rupees-per-share-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国炙手可热的涨势需要喘口气，等待刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-09/</link><description>由于投资者对中国经济复苏的热情减弱，中国股市周三下跌，大宗商品大幅下跌，而大盘则因美国经济能够避免衰退并支持全球需求的预期而企稳。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 02:17:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>投资者等待新线索，中国股市涨势放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-fall-sharply-set-snap-winning-streak-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国股市周三与香港股市一起暴跌，原因是投资者在大幅上涨后获利了结，而且官员未能激发人们对旨在重振经济的刺激计划的信心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:53:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-fall-sharply-set-snap-winning-streak-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国在重要讲话前称台湾总统正在加剧紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-is-escalating-tensions-china-says-ahead-key-speech-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国政府表示，台湾总统赖清德正在以“险恶的意图”加剧紧张局势，而赖清德将在台北发表主题演讲，这可能会引发中国的军事反应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 00:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-is-escalating-tensions-china-says-ahead-key-speech-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>优衣库所有者预计品牌海外扩张推动年利润飙升 24%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-owner-seen-posting-24-annual-profit-surge-brands-overseas-push-2024-10-08/</link><description>随着品牌进军西方市场以及中国业务的复苏，休闲服装巨头优衣库的日本所有者预计将连续第三年超出自己的预期，实现创纪录的利润。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 23:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uniqlo-owner-seen-posting-24-annual-profit-surge-brands-overseas-push-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>日本制造商十月份信心上升，对中国的担忧挥之不去：路透社短观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-manufacturers-confidence-rises-oct-concerns-over-china-linger-2024-10-08/</link><description>路透社周三的月度调查显示，日本制造商对 10 月份的商业状况变得更加有信心，但他们对中国经济复苏的步伐仍持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 23:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-manufacturers-confidence-rises-oct-concerns-over-china-linger-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：投资者解读美联储茶叶，摆脱中国刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-08/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 21:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪预计 2025 年墨西哥电动汽车销量将增至 10 万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-sees-ev-mexico-sales-ramping-up-100000-2025-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪墨西哥公司负责人 Jorge Vallejo 周二表示，该公司预计今年将在墨西哥销售 5 万辆电动汽车 (EV)，并于 2025 年销售 10 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 20:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-sees-ev-mexico-sales-ramping-up-100000-2025-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国商务部称雷蒙多与中国商务部长通话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/raimondo-speaks-with-chinas-commerce-minister-us-commerce-dept-says-2024-10-08/</link><description>美国商务部表示，美国商务部长吉娜·雷蒙多周二与中国商务部部长王文涛通话，讨论了上个月举行的商业问题双边工作组会议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/raimondo-speaks-with-chinas-commerce-minister-us-commerce-dept-says-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：布鲁塞尔在电动汽车纠纷中拒绝了中国关于最低销售价格3万欧元的提议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-rejected-china-proposal-30000-euro-minimum-sales-price-ev-dispute-2024-10-08/</link><description>三名消息人士称，布鲁塞尔拒绝了中国政府关于中国制造的进口电动汽车售价最低为 30,000 欧元（32,946 美元）的提议，北京方面希望此举能避免欧盟下个月征收关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-rejected-china-proposal-30000-euro-minimum-sales-price-ev-dispute-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok被13个州和华盛顿特区起诉，被指控伤害年轻用户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</link><description>TikTok 周二面临美国 13 个州和哥伦比亚特区提起的新诉讼，指控这个流行的社交媒体平台伤害并未能保护年轻人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>